Subject: RE: [T2] RE: Coils

  I had a coil that was failing in a Mercedes. (Bosch Blue) It ran fine
until it warmed up then it would miss regularly. I was working for an older
guy who said that if it only missed when warm that was the first thing to
try. Replaced the coil and that was it.

